PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of BOYD WARNER of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Marilyn Backman.
